{"tid":224134,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"電影推介 四月是你的謊言","createTime":"2017-04-30T18:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T09:41:58.000Z","uid":109318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5745be76329a56cfabb9ac6f014e6feed38c0736","tid":224134,"uid":109318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:32:10.000Z","msg":"覺得套戲都係傳統日本電影feel<br />\n套戲取景 色調 配樂都係突出之處（男主角算幾靚仔）<br />\n可能無睇過漫畫 覺得套戲都幾平淡 但就係最鍾意日本電影lee 種平淡 同埋套戲前半段講母親之情都幾好<br />\n係套戲可以感覺到淡淡嫁青春同戀愛<br />\n缺點係女主角唔靚同埋男主角好似愛得太遲or feel唔到有幾愛女主角<br />\n值得一睇 我見IMDb都有7.3分"},{"pid":"e4e7115ec423e7229dc64311afc24b61374461a9","tid":224134,"uid":4058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"賢人上年拍好多戲/劇 完全代入唔到嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 絲絲都唔靚？"},{"pid":"c424e518fb5f0bce9c768775c0347939e0840ef8","tid":224134,"uid":109318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賢人上年拍好多戲/劇 完全代入唔到嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 絲絲都唔靚？</blockquote><br />\n絲絲係女主角？<br />\n廣瀨鈴做女主 我見黑黑地 個樣真係唔多靚"},{"pid":"f2462ca7a3802b09e71bac83893c090ad39bdef8","tid":224134,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"套套都係山崎賢人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d799358fb152bbea84b6cbada3a812e06a048f3","tid":224134,"uid":4058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賢人上年拍好多戲/劇 完全代入唔到嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 絲絲都唔靚？</blockquote><br />\n絲絲係女主角？<br />\n廣瀨鈴做女主 我見黑黑地 個樣真係唔多靚</blockquote><br />\n譯名唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地應該係講緊同一個人 我覺得佢其他造型好好多<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/030713_fd3148d8974bdddfddbf5163b558a985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F030713_fd3148d8974bdddfddbf5163b558a985.jpg&h=77b486ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b2551ab49f51159ee9fc26032c21166ee5d9c83","tid":224134,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T20:27:16.000Z","msg":"電影唯一好過漫畫係冇禁多回你死老母個帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過電影冇左最尾公生果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n春天  就要來了<br />\n和你相遇的春天就要來了<br />\n再也沒有你的春天  就要來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0056da670d24a339dda7f7383ed6b10b6b53a364","tid":224134,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電影唯一好過漫畫係冇禁多回你死老母個帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過電影冇左最尾公生果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">春天  就要來了<br />\n和你相遇的春天就要來了<br />\n再也沒有你的春天  就要來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}